text: {'text': 'Serving the muslim community in Bt. Panjang & surrounding areas since 2003. Big spacious prayer hall with modern ammenities. Constant upgrading & upkeep have kept the mosque in good condition. Bangkit LRT Station is the nearest to the mosque. Public carpark available opposite the mosque.', 'languageCode': 'en'}

name: places/ChIJ_3Y3IacR2jERDZXytCvH7Do/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURyN2VLeUtREAE
text: {'text': "Al-Iman Mosque is Bukit Panjang's gem for the Muslim community to go for their daily and Friday Prayers. It is also a venue for the community to come together for lectures or syarahan and Islamic education. The mosque is served by Bukit Panjang LRT at BP9 Bangkit.", 'languageCode': 'en'}
